parameters.name: If-Match
parameters.description: The header that is used to ensure that the changed resources are consistent with resources to be changed. The value comes from the response of the Create, Get, and Update API operations.

parameters.name: X-Fc-Account-Id
parameters.description: The ID of your Alibaba Cloud account.

parameters.name: X-Fc-Date
parameters.description: The time when the function is invoked. The value is in the **EEE,d MMM yyyy HH:mm:ss GMT** format.

parameters.name: X-Fc-Trace-Id
parameters.description: The trace ID of the request for Function Compute API. The value is the same as that of the requestId parameter in the response.
